                <ul class="ulInstr">
                  <li class="liInstr">Upon hitting the start button below, you will be presented with the names of U.S. States in random order â€“ and a timer will start!</li>
                  <li class="liInstr">State names that by chance land in their sort order position are removed from play and appear as faded entries.</li>
